<Barbarossa41DeBr> <Heeresgruppe Mitte is advancing on Smolensk, a main city on the road to Moscow exactly on the main axis of advance. The Soviets are known to have staked a lot into the defence of this city, at least six fresh Soviet armies equipped with modern weapons have been spotted in the area, and for the first time since the early days of this campaign, the Soviet air force is very active again. It looks as if the Soviet high command has selected the area around the city as the place for a major delaying action. Heeresgruppe Mitte will attempt to envelop the bulk of the Soviet forces near Orsha in yet another annihilation battle. Luftflotte 2, with Fliegerkorps II and VIII, will support this by breaking the concentration of Soviet airpower in this area and then by isolating the battlefield from the air and flying close support. The battle ahead may be decisive for the entire war!>
<Barbarossa41DeDb> <Heeresgruppe Mitte has won a total victory in the Smolensk area! The bulk of the Soviet forces were enveloped and annihilated at Orsha and Yelnya, with yet another half million prisoners and thousands of guns and tanks captured. Luftflotte 2 was the key to this success, as the constant and accurate air support helped to halt the Soviet counterattack at Rogachev and managed to win air superiority against a strong force of Soviet fighter and bomber units, which for the first time since June tried to actively challenge the Luftwaffe. That challenge failed and the Soviet air strength in the central front has been all but annihilated, as has been the majority of Soviet armoured strength. Heeresgruppe Mitte moves onwards to Moscow!>
<Barbarossa41RuBr> <The German forces on the central front are approaching Smolensk. Stavka has decided to try and hold the enemy advance in this area. For this operation, six fresh armies have been committed, as well as strong VVS reserves, including 6 IAK of the Moscow PVO. For success in the upcoming battle, it is absolutely necessary to break the German air superiority. For the first time since the attack in June, we are under orders directly challenge the German Luftwaffe! Strong reinforcements, most notably many regiments equipped with the latest Yakovlev and LaGG fighters, as well as many of the new armoured attack aircraft Il-2 have been deployed to the area around Smolensk. Once air supremacy is established, we will be able to halt or even turn back the German aggression!>
<Barbarossa41RuDb> <Due to many failures on division and corps command level, the German armies were able to envelop Red Army forces at Orsha and annihilate them, but only at a severe cost of their own. The VVS in the Smolensk area has been dealt severe losses in extremely hard fighting, but managed to maintain local superiority, even if only for a limited time. The new plane types have proved to be very effective. While as a whole the battle was a defeat, the sacrifice of our comrades at Smolensk has bought precious time to strengthen the defence of Moscow.>
