<Kerch42DeDb> <Our blitzkrieg assault overwhelmed the Soviet defences, and we were able to destroy many of their aircraft on the ground.  The final attacks on the army trapped at Kerch may have cost the Soviets up to quarter of a million troops which will not be available to counter Operation Blau.  The Red Navy has also suffered heavily, and it seems likely that our renewed bombardment of Sevastopol will at last capture that fortress.  Luftflotte 4 was able to secure a level of control not achieved since last summer, though we sustained more losses than before.>   
