<Orel43DeBr> <The collapse of the German army after Stalingrad continued into February.  The Soviets are threatening the supply lines of our Rzhev armies and the salient is to be evacuated and devastated early in March.  Our troops have to hold on south of Orel while forces are scraped up to cut off the Soviet penetration to the west.  Manstein's counterattacks in the south may help, by drawing some of the enemy forces away.> 
