<Ukraine44RuDb> <The Red Army successfully took Lvov and managed to cross the Dukla pass over the Carpathians into Hungary. A Hungarian attempt to negotiate a separate peace was crushed by the Germans, turning a satellite state into another occupied country. The Hungarian military however fights on. Once again, the VVS was very successful in supporting the advance and gained air supremacy over both Hungarian and German enemies.>
