<Leningrad42WinterDeBr> <After the difficult battles at Demyansk and Volkhov, the siege ring around Leningrad has been closed again. The only supply route for the city is the Ladogasee. During winter, the Soviets are sending truck convoys over the ice. Luftflotte 1 has the grim mission of keeping the pressure on Leningrad, both by maintaining air supremacy and striking at Soviet industry and supplies.>
<Leningrad42WinterRuBr> <The efforts by the Red Army to re-establish the land connection to Leningrad have failed. The city still is in a difficult position, even though the supplies brought in via Lake Ladoga are now barely sufficient to sustain the civilians and soldiers in Leningrad. The main task of the VVS will for the next time will be to keep the city alive. For this, we have to protect our supply routes from air attacks, strike at the enemy positions and protect the city itself.>
